function response (room, msg, sender, igc, replier) {

​

function ftn (f) { // Fraction To Number

if (!f.includes("/")) return;

sp = f.split("/");

return Number(sp[0]) / Number(sp[1]);

}

if (msg.startsWith("/그래프")) {

let input = msg.substr(4).trim().split(",");

let arr = [];

input.forEach(e => {

e = e.replace(/ /g, "");

(!e.startsWith("x=") && !e.includes("y")) && (e = "y=" + e);

if (e.startsWith("x=")) {

n = e.split("=")[1];

n = isNaN(n) && n.includes("/") ? ftn(n) : Number(n);

arr.push({"X": [n, 255, 0, 0]});

} else if (!e.includes("x")) {

n = e.split("=")[1];

n = isNaN(n) && n.includes("/") ? ftn(n) : Number(n);

arr.push({"L": [0, n, 255, 0, 0]});

} else if (e.includes("x") && ["^", "²", "sin", "cos", "tan"].every(r => !e.includes(r))) {

a = e.split("x")[0].split("=")[1];

a = a || 1;

b = e.split("x")[1];

b = b || 0;

a = isNaN(a) && a.includes("/") ? ftn(a) : Number(a);

b = isNaN(b) && b.includes("/") ? ftn(b) : Number(b);

arr.push({"L": [a, b, 0, 0, 255]});

} else if (e.split(/x\^2|x²/).length == 2 && !e.substr(2).includes("y")) {

a = e.split(/x\^2|x²/)[0].split("=")[1];

a = a || 1;

if (e.split("x").length == 3) {

b = e.split(/x\^2|x²/)[1].split("x")[0];

c = e.split("x")[2];

} else {

b = 0;

c = 0;

}

a = isNaN(a) && a.includes("/") ? ftn(a) : Number(a);

b = isNaN(b) && b.includes("/") ? ftn(b) : Number(b);

c = isNaN(c) && c.includes("/") ? ftn(c) : Number(c);

arr.push({"Q": [a, b, c, 0, 255, 0]});

} else if (e.replace(/\^2/g, "²").split("²").length == 3) {

if (e.includes("(x")) {

a = -Number(e.split("(x")[1].split(")")[0]);

} else a = 0;

if (e.includes("(y")) {

b = -Number(e.split("(y")[1].split(")")[0]);

} else b = 0;

r = Math.sqrt(Number(e.split("=")[1]));

arr.push({"C": [a, b, r, 0, 0, 0]});

} else if (e.includes("sin(")) {

a = e.split("sin(")[0].split("y=")[1];

a = a || 1;

b = e.split("sin(")[1].split("x)")[0];

b = b || 1;

c = e.split(")")[1];

c = c || 0;

a = isNaN(a) && a.includes("/") ? ftn(a) : Number(a);

b = isNaN(b) && b.includes("/") ? ftn(b) : Number(b);

c = isNaN(c) && c.includes("/") ? ftn(c) : Number(c);

arr.push({"S": [a, b, c, 0, 0, 0]});

} else if (e.includes("cos(")) {

a = e.split("cos(")[0].split("y=")[1];

a = a || 1;

b = e.split("cos(")[1].split("x)")[0];

b = b || 1;

c = e.split(")")[1];

c = c || 0;

a = isNaN(a) && a.includes("/") ? ftn(a) : Number(a);

b = isNaN(b) && b.includes("/") ? ftn(b) : Number(b);

c = isNaN(c) && c.includes("/") ? ftn(c) : Number(c);

arr.push({"CO": [a, b, c, 0, 0, 0]});

} else if (e.includes("tan(")) {

a = e.split("tan(")[0].split("y=")[1];

a = a || 1;

b = e.split("tan(")[1].split("x)")[0];

b = b || 1;

c = e.split(")")[1];

c = c || 0;

a = isNaN(a) && a.includes("/") ? ftn(a) : Number(a);

b = isNaN(b) && b.includes("/") ? ftn(b) : Number(b);

c = isNaN(c) && c.includes("/") ? ftn(c) : Number(c);

arr.push({"T": [a, b, c, 0, 0, 0]});

} else {

arr.push("X");

replier.reply("• 제공되지 않는 식 표현입니다.");

}

});

if (arr.indexOf("X") == -1) {

// replier.reply(JSON.stringify(arr));

link = drawGraph(room, arr);

// replier.reply(link);

}

}

​

}

​

​

drawGraph = (room, arr) => {

link = Jsoup.connect("http://doami.dothome.co.kr/drawGraph.php")

.data("coor", JSON.stringify(arr)).post().text();

sendImg(room, link);

return link;

}
